@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ijjoma(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = v1
    v1 = (((v0 + 0.80 / v2 + 0.56) * (v1 + 0.23 / tmp + 0.12)) - (v0 - wp.abs(v0 + 0.79)))
    v0 = tmp
    v2 = v2
    v0 = wp.sin(v2)
    v0 = ((v1 * wp.cos(v2 + 0.67)) + v0)
    data[tid] = v0
